oc:kn_863323cc a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:KnownIssue ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When processing long documents, scanned PDFs, or complex layouts" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Very large PDFs (500+ pages) may need chunking. Complex layouts with tables may need reformatting. Multi-column text is processed left-to-right. Handwritten content recognition is limited." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These are documented limitations that affect output quality and should be communicated to the user." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_9d0dbee0 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When processing any PDF document" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Cannot execute embedded PDF code, process password-protected PDFs without a password, guarantee 100% OCR accuracy on scanned documents, or numerically analyze charts and images." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These are hard technical limitations of the underlying extraction tools and OCR engines." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_b9fb4c24 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When formulating questions or extraction requests for PDF content" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use specific, targeted questions over broad ones. Reference sections by number, specify desired output format, name exact fields to extract, and set filtering criteria." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Specific queries yield more accurate and useful answers than vague, broad questions." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_d94a2e83 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:WorkflowStrategy ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When analyzing documents over 50 pages" ;
    oc:directiveContent "For long documents, ask about specific sections for accuracy rather than requesting whole-document analysis. Use page-by-page summaries for overview, then drill into areas of interest." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Chunked analysis improves accuracy and reduces hallucination risk compared to whole-document processing." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_e42cf6aa a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:SecurityImplication ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When handling sensitive, confidential, or regulated documents" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Document contents are processed according to the AI provider's privacy policy. For sensitive documents, recommend on-premise solutions, redacting sensitive information first, or checking data retention policies." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Users must understand that PDF content may be transmitted to and stored by the AI provider." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

